help with mr clean mop and other mops i have the mr clean magic eraser mop and i don't really like it it doesn't really seem to clean very well after i use it i can get a damp paper towel and wipe the floor and the paper towel is dirty i usually get on my hands and knees after using the mr clean mop and wipe the entire kitchen floor down again with lysol kitchen spray and paper towels until it's clean the mop seems to pick up a little of the dirt but smear the rest around i found the same to be true with the swiffer wet too what do you think of the mr clean mop am i the only one who doesn't care for it i need a better mop i have a year old son i have to have a clean kitchen floor anyone have advice on mops what is a good mop that cleans well i have a linoleum floor if that makes a difference buy yourself an ordinary mop plus mope bucket add hot water and floor cleaner eg flash dont make it too soapy wet all your floor then rinse with your squeezed out mop open window and leave to dry hey presto nice clean floor Vacuum cleaner Menstrual cup Dishwashing Sento Upholstery Hand washing Towel Fire fighting Textile manufacturing Soap Dry cleaning Wok Manicure Japanese tea ceremony Toilet paper Dishwasher Fire extinguisher Dairy Paper Kitchen Printmaking Paper towel Bulk vending Brewery Blood Simple Basement Aerial (dance move) Cast iron Fecal incontinence Customs and etiquette of Japan Hat Social rule Diseases of the honeybee Drag racing Tattoo Soldering Kimberly-Clark Corporation Toilet Urinal M16 (rifle) Genericized trademark Sauna RuneScape quests Diving suit Drill bit Violin Bacon Diablo II: Lord of Destruction Jam (TV series) Hydrogen peroxide Casting Fuel injection Vinegar Nuggets: Original Artyfacts from the First Psychedelic Era, 1965-1968 Detergent Red Dwarf characters Dialysis Laundry Reckitt Benckiser Towelie Justification (theology) Hazing Charlie and the Chocolate Factory (film) Hamster Tag Glossary of climbing terms The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy Primar